Serial TCPServer and simple TCPClient. Transfer file from server to client.

USAGE:
  $ ruby server.rb hostname port filename
  $ ruby client.rb hostname port filename
  
hostname - specifies hostname for server
port - specifies port for server
filename - specifies file to send (recieve)

RUNNING:
  Try start server in one terminal window and start client in another.
  Type this:
  $ ruby server.rb 127.0.0.1 4455 ./input.pdf
  # ruby client.rb 127.0.0.1 4455 ./output.pdf
